Git : Will work as local repository 

Git Hub : is a remote repository

go inside the project location for mac you can go inside the project location
by using the terminal


git init : it will intialize the empty repository
if you want to add the single file
you can do git add filename
or if you want to add more files at single time 
you can say git add .
git add README.md
git commit -m "first commit"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/shiavaregalla99/MagentoProject.git
git push -u origin main